1
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:50,079
It's so delicious!

2
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,880
Delicious.

3
00:01:34,559 --> 00:01:35,960
It was you, wasn't it, Saturn?

4
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:37,760
Khun Pakin

5
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,320
This dinner

6
00:01:41,639 --> 00:01:42,639
you cooked it, didn't you?

7
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,079
No, I didn't.

8
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:44,679
Liar!

9
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,880
I grew up eating Aunt Tammy's food.

10
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,159
I know exactly what it's like.

11
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,840
It tastes just like what you had.

12
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:57,559
Just barely edible enough
to keep you alive.

13
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,079
But Aunt Tammy...

14
00:02:05,639 --> 00:02:07,000
she saved our lives.

15
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,920
Because of her terrible cooking

16
00:02:11,559 --> 00:02:13,119
we were able to survive.

17
00:02:16,239 --> 00:02:17,159
We ate just to fill our stomachs.

18
00:02:18,679 --> 00:02:19,960
Just to have enough energy to work.

19
00:02:21,679 --> 00:02:23,159
We didn't care about the taste.

20
00:02:24,559 --> 00:02:25,559
Unlike this dinner tonight.

21
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,239
It's the most delicious thing

22
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:32,199
I've ever had in my entire life.

23
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:38,719
I just

24
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,280
wanted to do something nice

25
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,760
for you, Khun Pakin. That's all.

26
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:44,400
Hoping that maybe

27
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,400
the anger and hatred in your heart

28
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,920
might subside, even just a little.

29
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:53,880
Yeah.

30
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:58,320
It's so delicious that
it makes me miss my brother.

31
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:00,800
Pakinai must have

32
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,559
tasted the delicious food

33
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,000
made by you.

34
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:07,079
But now

35
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,039
he can't do that anymore.

36
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:10,480
And it's because of you.

37
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,079
It's all because of you.

38
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,440
Besides the delicious food

39
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,519
that you cooked for my brother

40
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,559
what else is there in you

41
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:19,239
that made my brother
so utterly obsessed with you?

42
00:03:20,119 --> 00:03:22,000
To the point of willingly dying for you.

43
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,519
Your pretty face?

44
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:27,519
Those pleading eyes?

45
00:03:29,119 --> 00:03:30,320
Or your mouth?

46
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,079
or even your kiss?

47
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,360
You can't do this to me!

48
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,480
You dare slap me?!

49
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:39,960
Huh?

50
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:40,679
Yes!

51
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,920
It's because of your kiss

52
00:03:42,239 --> 00:03:43,199
There must be more to it than that.

53
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:43,599
Don't

54
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,320
I need to find out.

55
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:44,679
Don't!

56
00:03:44,679 --> 00:03:45,480
Every single part of your body

57
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,719
that you used to seduce my brother!

58
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:48,639
Don't!

59
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:49,719
Khun Pakin!

60
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:50,960
Don't!

61
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,320
Don't!

62
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:12,159
Thank you all for gathering here.

63
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,920
I have an important matter

64
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,880
that I want to announce to everyone.

65
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,440
Regarding the top executive position

66
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,679
of our hotel

67
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:22,320
and the Prakayfah Pradabdao
conglomerate.

68
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:23,880
Madame.

69
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,639
Isn't this a bit too rushed?

70
00:04:28,559 --> 00:04:29,679
The truth is plain to see.

71
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,760
Why should we wait?

72
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,280
At the very least

73
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,079
we should wait

74
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:34,719
for Khun Venus

75
00:04:34,719 --> 00:04:36,119
and Khun Saturn to return.

76
00:04:36,119 --> 00:04:37,880
Give them a chance to tell the truth.

77
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:38,880
About what really

78
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,079
happened.

79
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:40,880
There's no need.

80
00:04:41,239 --> 00:04:42,719
I'll be frank.

81
00:04:42,719 --> 00:04:45,079
I am very tired, and I just want to rest.

82
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,639
That's exactly why

83
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:49,280
I wanted to make the decision

84
00:04:49,599 --> 00:04:52,480
to hand over the business
to Venus and Saturn

85
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,960
for them to take over

86
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,079
But those two boys have
deeply disappointed me.

87
00:04:59,239 --> 00:05:01,559
No matter how much
I love my grandsons

88
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,360
I will never allow

89
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,880
those kids to squander my fortune.

90
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:09,639
That's why I invited the lawyer here

91
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:11,119
to draw up new documents for me.

92
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:13,400
And the moment
I sign those documents

93
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:16,320
everything will be under
Khaeng Khae's control.

94
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,559
Madame

95
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,480
In that case, I will go
prepare the documents for you.

96
00:05:40,239 --> 00:05:41,119
Damn it.

97
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,360
Why did it have to turn out like this

98
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,239
Oh, Madame...

99
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,679
No.

100
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,039
I'm not going to let this happen.

101
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:57,079
Wait, P'Mawin.

102
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:57,920
Where are you going?

103
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,320
Step aside, Lookkai.

104
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:00,360
Where are you going?

105
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,079
Or do you want to come with me?

106
00:06:03,599 --> 00:06:05,159
I'm going to tell Madame to change her mind.

107
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:07,679
Tell her not to fall into the trap

108
00:06:08,039 --> 00:06:10,079
that Khaeng Khae, your mother, has set.

109
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,599
Lookkai.

110
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:14,800
Did you not hear what I said?

111
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,360
Or maybe...

112
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,840
you're actually an accomplice
to your mother's scheme?

113
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,000
Are you happy

114
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,639
that your mother

115
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,039
will get everything she wants?

116
00:06:30,719 --> 00:06:31,920
How I feel

117
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,639
doesn't matter.

118
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,119
All I have to do

119
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,119
is follow my mother's orders.

120
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,800
I've never had a life of my own.

121
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,519
Never.

122
00:06:44,039 --> 00:06:45,679
Not even when it comes to us.

123
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,199
Lookkai.

124
00:06:58,400 --> 00:06:59,880
If my mother finds out

125
00:07:00,119 --> 00:07:00,760
we're dating

126
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,360
she will never accept it.

127
00:07:05,679 --> 00:07:06,760
We will never be able to

128
00:07:08,039 --> 00:07:09,480
see each other again.

129
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,400
Lookkai.

130
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:46,679
Lookkai.

131
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,440
Let's help each other.

132
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,840
Help me do what's right.

133
00:07:55,719 --> 00:07:56,840
Uncover the truth.

134
00:07:58,639 --> 00:07:59,519
About what really happened

135
00:08:00,559 --> 00:08:01,920
to Khun Venus

136
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,800
and Khun Saturn.

137
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:05,159
We have to find them
as soon as possible.

138
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,519
Before the handover
contract is signed.

139
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,480
Because if this all goes

140
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:13,000
according to Khaeng Khae's plan

141
00:08:14,679 --> 00:08:15,199
Do you know

142
00:08:16,159 --> 00:08:17,840
who the next victim will be?

143
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,079
It will be Khun Dao Kang Fah.

144
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,279
I understand.

145
00:08:47,359 --> 00:08:48,680
What's the matter with you

146
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,239
huh?

147
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,560
Spacing out and daydreaming like that.

148
00:08:52,079 --> 00:08:54,319
You're acting just like...

149
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:58,920
like me right after I lost my virginity.

150
00:08:59,600 --> 00:08:59,960
Yes?

151
00:09:00,319 --> 00:09:00,680
Huh?

152
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,960
It's nothing.

153
00:09:04,319 --> 00:09:05,159
Really nothing.

154
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,079
Wait, wait, wait.

155
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,479
Looking like this...

156
00:09:09,479 --> 00:09:10,199
Don't tell me

157
00:09:10,199 --> 00:09:11,359
don't you dare tell me

158
00:09:11,359 --> 00:09:13,039
that the two of you

159
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,439
already did 'it'.

160
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,960
There's really nothing going on.

161
00:09:20,479 --> 00:09:22,680
You're really something else.

162
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,199
Looking all quiet and innocent like this

163
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:27,399
but you bagged both

164
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,920
the younger and the older brother,
didn't you?

165
00:09:31,319 --> 00:09:32,560
It's not like that.

166
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,840
It's nothing.

167
00:09:34,319 --> 00:09:35,840
Not like this, not like that.

168
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,439
Then how is it, huh?

169
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,640
Tell me.

170
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:41,880
Well

171
00:09:42,359 --> 00:09:43,079
everything that happened

172
00:09:43,079 --> 00:09:44,199
didn't mean anything.

173
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,880
It happened out of revenge

174
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,199
not love.

175
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,399
Love?

176
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,039
Don't even think about it.

177
00:09:50,479 --> 00:09:51,119
Pakin

178
00:09:51,119 --> 00:09:52,199
will never love you.

179
00:09:53,119 --> 00:09:54,119
He only has revenge in his heart.

180
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,880
But what about you?

181
00:09:58,399 --> 00:10:00,239
How do you feel about him?

182
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,239
Well

183
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,000
about that

184
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,119
I'm still not entirely sure.

185
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,479
But one thing is for sure

186
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,359
I understand exactly how he feels.

187
00:10:11,319 --> 00:10:12,680
Having to lose his brother

188
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,800
the person he fought side by side with

189
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:17,119
through this cruel world.

190
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:18,880
In a world

191
00:10:19,119 --> 00:10:20,840
that never showed them any mercy.

192
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,720
Because if it were me

193
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,000
I would be angry too.

194
00:10:27,119 --> 00:10:28,640
I would be just as vengeful as him.

195
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,399
And I might have had no choice

196
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:33,319
but to do the exact same thing

197
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,359
that he's doing to me.

198
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,079
Good.

199
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,079
It's good that you understand.

200
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,399
But revenge

201
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,920
is still revenge.

202
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:47,399
And hell

203
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,439
is still hell.

204
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:49,800
Nothing

205
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:51,640
can extinguish the fire of his vengeance.

206
00:10:56,239 --> 00:10:56,720
Well

207
00:10:57,239 --> 00:10:59,119
if this is the sin I must pay for

208
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,039
then I will endure it.
